cdata.name: Ronaldinho Soccer Coin
cdata.desc: Ronaldinho Soccer Coin (RSC) is a Neo-based cryptocurrency created by the famous football player Ronaldinho Gaúcho. It is a cryptocurrency designed only for the football market. The NEO-based RSC token will fuel a whole ecosystem called Planet RSC, which comprises the Ronaldinho Football Academy, Smile Project, a betting marketplace, Ronaldinho digital stadiums, and more.
